quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,WHEN EARTH is rocked in her last convulsion
  99,2,when Earth shakes off her burdens
  99,3,"and Man says, ‘What may this mean?‘ ―"
  99,4,on that day she will proclaim her tidings
  99,5,for your Lord will have inspired her
  99,6,On that day mankind will come out in broken bands to be shown their labours
  99,7,Whoever did an atom‘s weight of good shall see it
  99,8,and whoever did an atom‘s weight of evil shall also see it